questions.scenario:
You are debugging a production issue where a Spring Boot application processing bulk data imports is experiencing an `OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space`. The following service logic is used:

java
@Service
public class DataImportService {
    @PersistenceContext
    private EntityManager entityManager;

    @Transactional
    public void processLargeBatch(List<DataRecord> records) {
        for (DataRecord record : records) {
            DataEntity entity = convertToEntity(record);
            entityManager.persist(entity);
            // Business logic here
        }
    }
}


Heap dumps show millions of `DataEntity` instances held by the `SessionImpl` (Hibernate's `PersistenceContext`).
